    {
      "uid": "7cb9b55c-4229-552f-86a5-7159e0838b35",
      "clause_number": "preamble",
      "kind": "preamble",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 1,
      "text": "CIRCULAR\nHO/(201)2026-DDHS-POD1 I/10421/2026 April 28, 2026\nTo,\nAll Registered Debenture Trustees,\nRecognized Stock Exchanges\nDear Sir/ Madam,\nSub: Extension of timeline for compliance with terms and conditions by\nDebenture Trustees for carrying out activities outside the purview of\nSEBI",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/apr-2026/1777434657240.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/apr-2026/extension-of-timeline-for-compliance-with-terms-and-conditions-by-debenture-trustees-for-carrying-out-activities-outside-the-purview-of-sebi_101152.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/e4b71f73-1777434657240.pdf",
        "sha256": "e4b71f73e089eae69d5ef57a241c2993fdbdea33bd977f9f6df1f44092c51030",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T12:04:49Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "dea65d1b-5083-5245-b206-4adc5a08995c",
      "clause_number": "1",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 2,
      "text": "1. On October 27, 2025, amendments to the SEBI (Debenture Trustees)\nRegulations, 1993 (“DT Regulations”) were notified, inter alia introducing\nRegulation 9C to provide clarity on the scope of permitted activities for Debenture\nTrustees (DTs). The provision inter-alia stipulates that a debenture trustee holding\na valid certificate of registration may transfer its activities that are not regulated by\nSEBI to separate business unit(s) within a period of six months from the date of\nnotification of the SEBI (Debenture Trustees) (Amendment) Regulations, 2025 in\nthe Official Gazette, or within such extended period as may be specified by the\nBoard.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/apr-2026/1777434657240.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/apr-2026/extension-of-timeline-for-compliance-with-terms-and-conditions-by-debenture-trustees-for-carrying-out-activities-outside-the-purview-of-sebi_101152.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/e4b71f73-1777434657240.pdf",
        "sha256": "e4b71f73e089eae69d5ef57a241c2993fdbdea33bd977f9f6df1f44092c51030",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T12:04:49Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "97af68df-91a0-571c-830c-24ceda7f1b44",
      "clause_number": "2",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 3,
      "text": "2. Subsequently, the operational framework, including the terms and conditions\ngoverning activities undertaken by debenture trustees, was prescribed vide SEBI\ncircular HO/17/11/12(3)2025-DDHS-POD1/ I/146/2025 dated November 25, 2025.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/apr-2026/1777434657240.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/apr-2026/extension-of-timeline-for-compliance-with-terms-and-conditions-by-debenture-trustees-for-carrying-out-activities-outside-the-purview-of-sebi_101152.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/e4b71f73-1777434657240.pdf",
        "sha256": "e4b71f73e089eae69d5ef57a241c2993fdbdea33bd977f9f6df1f44092c51030",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T12:04:49Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "231566cb-aff1-5b16-8985-a96e1f55ce7b",
      "clause_number": "3",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 4,
      "text": "3. Based on representations received from the industry highlighting operational\nchallenges in establishing the necessary systems and processes for effective\nimplementation, it has been decided to grant additional six months for compliance\nby the DTs. Accordingly, the provisions of the aforesaid amendment and circular\nshall be implemented by Debenture Trustees by October 27, 2026.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/apr-2026/1777434657240.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/apr-2026/extension-of-timeline-for-compliance-with-terms-and-conditions-by-debenture-trustees-for-carrying-out-activities-outside-the-purview-of-sebi_101152.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/e4b71f73-1777434657240.pdf",
        "sha256": "e4b71f73e089eae69d5ef57a241c2993fdbdea33bd977f9f6df1f44092c51030",
        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T12:04:49Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "e6a6dd48-19b5-579f-8bbc-0f2963aec082",
      "clause_number": "4",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 5,
      "text": "4. All other provisions of the SEBI Circular dated November 25, 2025 shall remain\nunchanged.",
      "metadata": {
        "regulator": "SEBI",
        "source_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/sebi_data/attachdocs/apr-2026/1777434657240.pdf",
        "source_page_url": "https://www.sebi.gov.in/legal/circulars/apr-2026/extension-of-timeline-for-compliance-with-terms-and-conditions-by-debenture-trustees-for-carrying-out-activities-outside-the-purview-of-sebi_101152.html",
        "raw_pdf_path": "../corpus/inbox/sebi/e4b71f73-1777434657240.pdf",
