        "downloaded_at": "2026-07-06T12:04:49Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "uid": "2ab8f4d3-3ec0-5278-8c8e-79ecda2d687f",
      "clause_number": "5",
      "kind": "numbered",
      "page": 1,
      "paragraph_index": 6,
      "text": "5. This circular is issued in exercise of powers conferred under Section 11(1) of\nSecurities and Exchange Board of India Act, 1992 and Regulation 2A of SEBI\n(Debenture Trustees) Regulations, 1993, to protect the interest of investors in\nsecurities and to promote the development of, and to regulate, the securities\nmarket.",
      "metadata": {
